### Tutor User Journey - Minimal API Requests

### 1. Register as Tutor
# @name register
POST https://localhost:9000/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tutor@avancira.com",
  "password": "Test@1234",
  "confirmPassword": "Test@1234",
  "userName": "John",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Smith"
}

###

### 2. Login
# @name login
POST https://localhost:9000/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tutor@avancira.com",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

###

### 3. Get Current User (to get user ID)
# @name currentUser
GET https://localhost:9000/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### 4. Complete Profile Information
PUT https://localhost:9000/api/users/profile
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

Id={{currentUser.response.body.id}}&FirstName=John&LastName=Smith&PhoneNumber=+1234567890&Bio=Experienced mathematics tutor with 5+ years of teaching experience&TimeZoneId=UTC&AddressCity=New York&AddressState=NY&AddressCountry=USA

###

### 6. Get Available Categories
# @name categories
GET https://localhost:9000/api/lesson/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### 7. Submit a Listing
POST https://localhost:9000/api/listings/create-listing
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Name"

Expert Mathematics Tutoring - All Levels
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Description"

Comprehensive math tutoring from basic arithmetic to advanced calculus
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="HourlyRate"

45.00
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="CategoryIds"

{{categories.response.body.results[0].id}}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### 8. View My Listings
# @name myListings
GET https://localhost:9000/api/listings/tutor-listings
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### 9. Update Listing Title
PUT https://localhost:9000/api/listings/{{myListings.response.body.data.results[0].id}}/update-title
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "title": "Expert Mathematics Tutoring - Updated"
}

###

### 10. View All Lessons (with filters)
GET https://localhost:9000/api/lessons?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### 11. Accept/Respond to Lesson Proposition
PUT https://localhost:9000/api/lessons/respondToProposition/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

true

###

### 12. View Specific Lessons with Student
GET https://localhost:9000/api/lessons/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/{{categories.response.body.results[0].id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### 13. Cancel a Lesson (if needed)
DELETE https://localhost:9000/api/lessons/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### 14. View Messages/Chat
GET https://localhost:9000/api/chats
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### 15. Send Message to Student
POST https://localhost:9000/api/chats/1/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "content": "Great job in today's lesson! Keep practicing the problems we discussed."
}

###

### 16. View Earnings/Wallet
GET https://localhost:9000/api/wallets
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### 17. View Reviews/Evaluations
GET https://localhost:9000/api/evaluations
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### 18. Update Profile Bio
PUT https://localhost:9000/api/users/profile
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

Id={{currentUser.response.body.id}}&Bio=Updated bio: Expert tutor available for online sessions

###

### 19. View Notifications
GET https://localhost:9000/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### 20. Get Current User Profile (Final Check)
GET https://localhost:9000/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###
